	default 0
	range 0 4
	---help---
		Specifies the timer mode:

		  0 -> Upcounting mode
		  1 -> Downcounting mode
		  2 -> Center-aligned mode 1
		  3 -> Center-aligned mode 2
		  4 -> Center-aligned mode 3

